(1, 'Soufflé ice cream', 'souffle-ice-cream-200-grams', 'Candy made from candy mass whipped on proteins, covered with chocolate icing, with the addition of cocoa powder and chocolate icing. ', 2, 3, '423 kcal', '1,5 g', '18,2 g', '11,5 g', '63,1 g', '46,83 g', 'Egg whites, cocoa, sugar, chocolate icing, almonds', '8', '2023-09-11 13:37:56', '2024-02-23 11:10:46', '8', '120 days', '/photos/2/products/1.png', 1, 'Bucuria | Soufflé ice cream (200 grams)', 'Bucuria | Soufflé ice cream (200 grams)', '', 'The composition contains allergens such as: almonds, milk, gluten, traces of soy, peanuts.', ''),
