(221, 1, 'textarea', 'Описание', 'Блок 3', 14, 3, 0, 'The factory is located in Chisinau, Moldova. The production facilities of the Bucuria confectionery factory are certified in accordance with the requirements of international food quality and safety standards. \n            \nThe Bucuria factory operates a quality management system that meets the requirements of ISO 9001:2008 and a food safety management system that meets the requirements of the ISO 22000:2005 standard, which is confirmed by the presence of certificates of conformity.'),
