(108, 1, 'textarea', 'Текст', '', 6, 2, 106, '[\"Since 1996, the Central Testing Laboratory has advanced its objective to demonstrate that it operates in a management system, that it has high technical competence and can generate technically valid results. The objective was met and the laboratory obtained the initial accreditation, according to the requirements of the international standard EN ISO\\/IEC 17025, on December 25, 1996.\\n\\nUntil now, the Central Testing Laboratory maintains, continuously improves a management system in accordance with the requirements of the SM EN ISO\\/IEC 17025:2018 standard\",\"Since 1996, the Central Testing Laboratory has advanced its objective to demonstrate that it operates in a management system, that it has high technical competence and can generate technically valid results. The objective was met and the laboratory obtained the initial accreditation, according to the requirements of the international standard EN ISO\\/IEC 17025, on December 25, 1996.\\n\\nUntil now, the Central Testing Laboratory maintains, continuously improves a management system in accordance with the requirements of the SM EN ISO\\/IEC 17025:2018 standard\"]'),
